HEADWORD: Ladys mantle
<hw>La"dy's man"tle</hw> <pr>(l⟦amac⟧"d⟦icr⟧z m⟦acr⟧n"t'l)</pr>.
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of rosaceous herbs
(<gen>Alchemilla</gen>), esp. the European <spn>Alchemilla
